### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">فَأَمَّا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَعَمِلُوا۟ ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ فَيُدْخِلُهُمْ رَبُّهُمْ فِى رَحْمَتِهِۦ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ هُوَ ٱلْفَوْزُ ٱلْمُبِينُ</span>

### English

As for those who believed and did good, their Lord will admit them into His mercy. That is ˹truly˺ the absolute triumph.